window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Edward Fasbender is a devil.</p> <p>He's my father's biggest rival. He takes what he wants, and he bows to no one.</p> <p>And now Edward Fasbender wants me.</p> <p>I didn't expect to want him back.</p> <p>Having him is not in the cards, not when a union with him would destroy my father. But that doesn't mean I can't play with him a bit.</p> <p>Except, I've never played against such a ruthless opponent. Edward is cold and vicious, and my blood has never run hotter.</p> <p>They say you should choose the devil you know, but I've always preferred long odds.</p> <p>Even if it'll get me slain.</p> <p><b>A dark and edgy romance story all in one bundle. Includes </b><b><i>Rivalry</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>Ruin</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>Revenge</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Rising</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
